a2010 |title=Archived copy |accessdate=2010-07-22 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100724055121/http://www.presidencia.pt/angola2010/ |archivedate=2010-07-24 |df= }} Retrieved 7-22-10</ref> 8th CPLP Summit (23 July). |- |{{Flag|Argentina}} |[[Mar del Plata]] |November |20th Ibero-American Summit. |}
